summary: This is my SweetFX preset for The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ffff00][size=4][i][u]You will not find something that looks this good that also maintains a vanilla-esque FPS average. 

[/u]This preset is perfect for performance, as I use it with my low-end and high-end setups.

This preset is not for everyone, but I personally enjoy it a lot and hope you all do as well. 
[u]I won't be changing anything.[/u]
Enjoy! 

- Parker Chace[/i][/size][/color]
author: parkerchace
